Text:
Firstly, thanks to Farmill for upping a great torrent.

@Tobias314: The update involved remastering the series for HDTV, rerecording the vocal tracks by most of the original cast and re-edited it to more closely follow the manga.

All the Blu-Rays both English and Japanese have an aspect ratio of 1.33:1 (4:3). This is what they were remastered to and the 16:9 versions you see on TV have been cropped to get this widescreen aspect ratio.
